column2: SELECT s.ObjID as #objid, s.ra, s.dec, s.l, s.b, s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u as u0, s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g as g0, s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_r as r0, (s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u) - (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) as umg, (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) - (s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_r) as gmr, sp.LOGGWBG as logg, sp.LOGGWBGUNC as logg_err, sp.FEHWBG as feh, sp.FEHWBGUNC as feh_err, sp.ELODIERVFINAL as vr, sp.ELODIERVFINALERR as vr_err INTO mydb.all_spec_bhbs FROM Star s JOIN sppParams sp ON s.ObjID = sp.BESTOBJID WHERE (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) - (s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_r) < # AND (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) - (s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_r) > # AND (s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u) - (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) < # AND (s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u) - (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) > # AND sp.LOGGWBG > # AND sp.LOGGWBG < # AND sciencePrimary = #
